      "text": "（でも、二年生のクラス……緊張……）\n（みんな、大人）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ sophomore class… is nervous…）\n（Everyone‚ grown-up）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3000000595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
