      "text": "（はっ！　さくらちゃん発見……）\n（おおおおおおおお……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh! I found Sakura-chan…）\n（O-O-O-O-O-O-O-Oh…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1999994237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5999994237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "（周りにお友達、沢山……）\n（私の知らないさくらちゃんは、人気者）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Friends around‚ so many…）\n（The Sakura-chan I don't know‚ is popular）",
        "id": ""
