      "text": "（心なしか、笑顔もいつもと違う……）\n（人気アイドルのオフショット……貴重）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Somehow‚ even smile is different than usual…）\n（Popular idol's off-shot… so precious）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.53333352,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14633.333146700004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
