      "text": "（こっそり、スマホで激写する……パシャ）\n（雑誌の記者さんの気持ち……少し分かった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sneakily‚ let's take a quick photo with my smartphone… click）\n（I can understand a little bit… how a magazine reporter feels）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1999968806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.9333307225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
