      "text": "（ふぅ……満足した、帰りますか……）\n（って、違うよね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Phew… I'm satisfied‚ should I go back…）\n（No‚ it's different）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9333307225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "（私は名誉ある伝令係。任務がある……）\n（いい加減行かないと。伝えるだけ……伝えるだけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I am an honorable messenger. I have a mission…）\n（I really should go now. Just tell… just tell）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5333307225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.5666640559
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
