      "text": "（{user}さん、ごめんなさい）\n（私はここまでです……目が回ってきた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sorry‚ {user}-san）\n（That's all for me… I'm getting dizzy）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4999973892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
