      "text": "はっ！　本当に本物さくらちゃん……そ、そう\n{user}さんから言づてを預かってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! A real Sakura-chan… y-yes\nI have a message from {user}-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7333434382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2666767715
