      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "上級生のクラスに来るの緊張したよね\nじゃあ一緒にお昼食べよ。まだトンカツサンドあるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were nervous about coming to the senior class\nThen‚ let's have lunch together. Maybe there's still some pork cutlet sandwiches",
        "id": ""
      },
